Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官谢加图支配的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里蠢动，是个可怕的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光等人得到导师古列夫的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互信互勉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人经过重重困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于得到传说中\N的矿物艾斯古托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们一面令创师普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼上性命铸造的武器成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面寻找魔神\N以求成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发踏上新的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，在目的地前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受命于神官谢加图的可怕敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正等待时机夺取小光等人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔神瑟列斯苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了呢，卡贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群魔法骑士会来这个海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要收拾她们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说和你无关吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴杰罗和比加也被她们杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是大家的同伴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，卡贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起收拾魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美丽的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…莫歌拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔神在这个海里!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是怪泉艾蒂露娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是又叫我们跳进去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫我们坐上去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听懂莫歌拿的话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它叫我们吃掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会兴奋起来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞起来了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撞上了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被肥皂泡包围着?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是水中套囊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!既然你能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一开始就使用啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不会以戏弄我们为乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是座…神殿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…好热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有空气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神在这座海底神殿里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，你为何知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，我们分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有特别奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦，小海呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你回应我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是间很大的房呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!你在里面吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光，小海的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙走出来了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿，小海会没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是[瑟列斯]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是只容\N传说的魔法骑士触摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条龙是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!完全关上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条龙是…传说的魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，只要令那部魔神苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能拯救锡菲罗!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能救出艾美诺公主呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你们成功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们竟敢杀死我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…\N全是我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是指给我们\N杀死的魔物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比加!别理她们!\N照我说的话做!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来就是你吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要替同伴报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你们好差劲啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾以前做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会输给这种姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你们是同伴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那种大婶才不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的同伴是魔物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕虫小技!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…魔法无效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里将会成为你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的…魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从异世界被召唤来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士的少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要在我面前展示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有资格驾御我的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示你有资格成为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔法骑士的强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强力的…心?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打不倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!攻击额前的宝石!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光，你有受伤吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事，别说那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这魔物的声音太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过份啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过份啊!\N竟敢伤害我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友? 那魔物是你的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊!这孩子是我的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴杰罗和比加也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说\N这么奇怪的生物不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是魔物，不可融洽相处!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人明白这群孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们竟敢伤害它们!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然能叫朋友攻击别人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友被我们所杀，被我们伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不在乎吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乎啊…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友受伤你会悲伤吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友有危险你想救它吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不珍惜朋友算什么重要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡贝拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么!?卡贝拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我!阿斯克特啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示你有资格成为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔法骑士的强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海你快点令魔神苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!不行啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管她们!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那魔物不是你能应付的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎可以!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是打倒神官谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此，你不可以死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也好，你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强力的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前展示你有资格成为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔法骑士的强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然叫我抛\N下小光和小风逃命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可以…\N那竟然就是强力的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那种事…\N我办不到!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之…龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢伤害小光和小风呢!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护之风!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又创造出一种魔法呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…一起战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…我也战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果叫我抛下小光和小风不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神这种东西…\N我不需要!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机…机器人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条龙是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神是巨大机器人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不能展示强力的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你关怀同伴的强力的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正式认同了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你刚才那番话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你克服了考验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考验?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海看来被魔神试探了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你没逃命而救了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他认同你是魔法骑士了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为大家能同心合力!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，你的心还未足以驾御我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你苏醒 成为\N真正的魔法骑士时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再在你面前出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护甲又成长了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!魔神苏醒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样，锡菲罗就有救了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成长的武器和魔神\N也已得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒谢加图!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放马过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那样 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一部魔神苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
